sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'Load' FLOAT, 'OLoad' FLOAT, 'FrameForwardingRate' INTEGER, 'RxLoad' FLOAT, 'FrameLoss' INTEGER, 'IterationResult' string default 'fail')

SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'OLoad', ROUND((RxRes.FrameCount)/((LastArrivalTime - FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) AS 'FrameForwardingRate', round(((((RxRes.L1BitCount / 1000000.0) / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) / ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad)) * 100.0), 2) AS 'RxLoad', DroppedFrameCount AS 'FrameLoss' FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle

UPDATE MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp SET IterationResult = 'pass' WHERE MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.rowid = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp) and FrameLoss = 0  AND FrameSize =

sql_statement.static: INSERT INTO MethRfc2889FrameBroadcast(FrameSize, Load, FrameLoss, FrameForwardingRate, RxLoad) SELECT MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.FrameSize, MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.Load, MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.FrameLoss, MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.FrameForwardingRate, MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.RxLoad FROM MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp, (SELECT FrameSize, MAX(Load) AS alLoad FROM MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp WHERE FrameLoss = 0 GROUP BY FrameSize) AS A  WHERE A.FrameSize = MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.FrameSize AND A.alLoad = MethRfc2889BroadcastIterationsTmp.Load
